{
  "stem": "18102.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 801.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And, of course, that was used for preserving whatever it was that my grandmother would preserve in the big jars that she would keep there, whether it was compote of some sort or sauerkraut or things like that pickles.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I would very seldom go in there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But-- and even less often, would go visit upstairs to my grandmother's room.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "That's the extent of the-- of the house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It wasn't very big.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But it-- it-- it was considered quite well-off for what we were.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a Jewish neighborhood, but not exclusively so.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[DRINKS] There were non-Jews in the neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But mostly, it was predominantly Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, in fact, and-- and not very far, a couple of houses down across the street lived a relative of ours.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "His name was-- I think it was Maier.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was an egg merchant, which I thought in later years when I became an egg trader at the Chicago Mercantile Exchange, I thought it was kind of funny.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because I was carrying forward the tradition in the family.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I once talked to my father about that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He laughed.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was a real merchant in terms of real eggs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was just trading futures.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But so they lived nearby.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And on occasion, I would visit their house, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I don't recall much about their house except that there was a very large table.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my-- whoever was the relative would sit me down to give me some food as soon as I entered the-- her premises.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The other feature that I do remember is that at the far end of the neighborhood was a small synagogue where I would only visit on rare occasions.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because my parents were not the religious type.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So I don't think we were members of the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
